          <li>2018.Feb, when the story began between two young people who are thousands of miles away from each other.<br>They kept talking with each other ever since.</li><br>
          <li>2018.Mar,like all the flowers began to blossom in the awake of spring, the affection between the two young gets stronger.<br>Finally on March.13th(or shall we say 14th due to the time difference),they became boyfreind and girlfriend.</li><br>
          <li>2018.April, at New York City did they first meet.</li><br>
          <li>2018.May, first time ever they travelled together by night bus to Canada.<br>First time ever for both of them to the land of Canada.</li><br>
          <li>2018.Jun, the separate was too hard for both of them, when the boy decided to spend his summer holiday first ever in Japan, with her.</li><br>
          <li>2018.July, they didnt want to be apart again but sadly, the boy had to go back to US to start working.<br>Luckily, thye would meet each other soon in Los Angeles</li><br>
          <li>2018.Oct, in the breeze of early autumn, she went to the airport and finally met her boy at LAX airport after two months.<br>Guess who was so stupid that lost THE mobile phone and didnt know how to enter the bnb.(lol)</li><br>
          <li>2018.Oct, when they finally arrived in their home in Pheonix after only 1h of flight. It was the best place ever in the world.</li><br>
          <li>2018.Dec, the year was about to end. The lovebird got the chance to spend the merry Christmas and happy New Year together!<br>It was a wonderful ear!</li>  <br>  
